1. Dataexploration.R          ← data loading
2. Model__Descriptive_Statistic.R  ← descriptive stats & distribution
3. Model_Specification_setting.R   ← static VaR/ES (HS, Normal, t, CF)
4. Model_Specification.R           ← dynamic models (EWMA, GARCH, eGARCH)
5. Backtesting.R                   ← backtesting tests
6. Exedance_forecast.R             ← PRIIP scenarios
